#: report/bugreport.h:76
#, c-format
msgid "Search <a href='%s'>a list of known issues</a> for similar problem. If so, update existing issue instead of creating a new one."
msgstr "在 <a href='%s'>已知问题列表</a> 中搜索类似问题。若存在，请更新现有问题而非创建新问题。"

#: report/bugreport.h:78
#, c-format
msgid "As you know, <a href='%s'>a forum</a> for users is available where you can discuss problems and find solutions."
msgstr "如您所知，我们为用户提供了 <a href='%s'>一个论坛</a>，您可以在那里讨论问题并寻找解决方案。"

#: report/bugreport.h:79
#, c-format
msgid "Please, join the community on <a href='%s'>Slack</a>. Here you can also pose the question and learn the latest news."
msgstr "请加入 <a href='%s'>Slack</a> 上的社区。在这里，您既可以提出问题，也能了解最新动态。"

#: report/bugreport.h:80
#, c-format
msgid "Read <a href='%s'>How to Report Bugs Effectively</a> for useful tips."
